1
00:00:00,499 --> 00:00:05,023
♪A little bit sorry for my love for you♪

2
00:00:05,023 --> 00:00:10,527
♪Sorry, I was a little late♪

3
00:00:10,527 --> 00:00:16,955
♪I really want the unconscious longing
to appear faster♪

4
00:00:16,955 --> 00:00:21,435
♪Can I get closer
and hear you say "I do" once more♪

5
00:00:21,435 --> 00:00:25,883
♪Holding hands, the scenery
in midsummer is a new journey♪

6
00:00:25,883 --> 00:00:30,794
♪The chapters of a fairy tale
are performed one after another♪

7
00:00:30,794 --> 00:00:34,843
♪The promised moment
will definitely not be forgotten♪

8
00:00:34,843 --> 00:00:39,378
♪Can I get closer and listen to
the frequency of your heartbeat♪

9
00:00:39,378 --> 00:00:43,675
♪Start the countdown 4321,
a new scenery♪

10
00:00:43,675 --> 00:00:48,440
♪I want to see all the scenes about you♪

11
00:00:48,440 --> 00:00:51,931
♪No need to miss you anymore♪

12
00:00:51,931 --> 00:00:55,611
♪Right by your side♪

13
00:00:57,257 --> 00:01:00,635
=Jin Secretary=

14
00:01:00,635 --> 00:01:03,323
=Episode 8=

15
00:01:03,433 --> 00:01:05,566
Mr. Zeng Huaishi gives us a speech.

16
00:01:21,766 --> 00:01:23,366
Good evening, everyone.

17
00:01:24,333 --> 00:01:28,608
Welcome to the 8th Elite Exchange
Meeting in Horton City.

18
00:01:29,466 --> 00:01:32,033
I am Zeng Huaishi, an investment
representative of Lihuai International.

19
00:01:36,533 --> 00:01:38,000
Since the first meeting,
we've been committed

20
00:01:38,433 --> 00:01:43,600
to creating a win-win business
exchange platform for Horton City.

21
00:01:44,766 --> 00:01:48,700
Through years of efforts, many individual
entrepreneurs, enterprises, and groups

22
00:01:49,000 --> 00:01:53,700
have gained more business opportunities
to expand business cooperation.

23
00:01:54,800 --> 00:01:58,700
In this period, Lihuai International
is looking for socially beneficial...

24
00:01:58,700 --> 00:02:00,300
Is he really that attractive?

25
00:02:00,300 --> 00:02:02,080
Companies to invest in.

26
00:02:02,080 --> 00:02:04,266
- Miss Jin.
- We hope to make a modest contribution

27
00:02:04,266 --> 00:02:06,333
- No, no.
- to the economic development.

28
00:02:06,600 --> 00:02:10,300
Everyone knows that we did
a lot of charity work last year.

29
00:02:10,433 --> 00:02:16,100
In this process, everyone has gradually
found inner peace.

30
00:02:53,152 --> 00:02:55,433
Mr. Zeng, may I talk to you?

31
00:02:58,266 --> 00:03:00,299
Mr. Lan, long time no see.

32
00:03:00,300 --> 00:03:01,800
Long time no see.

33
00:03:06,933 --> 00:03:07,800
How have you been lately?

34
00:03:08,200 --> 00:03:13,000
Quite well. Our company is currently
raising funds, so I want to talk to you.

35
00:03:14,433 --> 00:03:18,033
Mr. Lan, the Lan family
should not lack investment.

36
00:03:20,100 --> 00:03:23,033
You know the market is not good now.

37
00:03:23,033 --> 00:03:26,066
All S-level investment companies
are very cautious.

38
00:03:26,133 --> 00:03:29,056
Only when Lihuai International
invests will they follow.

39
00:03:29,792 --> 00:03:32,200
Other S-level companies already
have their own beauty brands.

40
00:03:32,766 --> 00:03:35,033
So the possibility of investment
is not great.

41
00:03:35,166 --> 00:03:39,500
You're right. We've read
the information you've sent us.

42
00:03:39,633 --> 00:03:43,533
But we demand more stability.
You should be very clear about this.

43
00:03:45,366 --> 00:03:48,400
But I also believe
that you have seen our strength.

44
00:03:49,100 --> 00:03:51,000
There's no doubt about your strength.

45
00:03:51,733 --> 00:03:54,933
It's just that you haven't
ranked among the top ten.

46
00:03:55,533 --> 00:03:58,833
Won't your company invest
in 20 companies?

47
00:03:59,366 --> 00:04:01,500
We prefer quality to quantity this year.

48
00:04:08,000 --> 00:04:11,166
Why can't our group
even rank among the top ten?

49
00:04:13,833 --> 00:04:14,633
Mr. Lan,

50
00:04:16,100 --> 00:04:17,100
in a family enterprise,

51
00:04:17,800 --> 00:04:19,733
individual rights override
company systems.

52
00:04:20,366 --> 00:04:22,500
Wealth is highly concentrated
in your top management.

53
00:04:22,700 --> 00:04:24,900
Besides, you haven't published
financial reports for three years.

54
00:04:25,433 --> 00:04:27,766
So even though you're
such a large family group,

55
00:04:28,566 --> 00:04:29,933
I don't think you have a bright future.

56
00:04:30,833 --> 00:04:31,699
Mr. Zeng.

57
00:04:33,633 --> 00:04:35,533
I think even if it's a family group,

58
00:04:35,766 --> 00:04:37,433
it can't be underestimated.

59
00:04:37,533 --> 00:04:40,733
Moreover, the status of WE Beauty Family
in Horton City is well-known.

60
00:04:40,900 --> 00:04:44,766
Mr. Lan is young and promising.

61
00:04:45,166 --> 00:04:46,800
How could there be no bright future?

62
00:04:47,600 --> 00:04:48,608
Miss Jin.

63
00:04:50,933 --> 00:04:51,800
We meet again?

64
00:04:54,633 --> 00:04:55,500
You know each other?

65
00:04:56,933 --> 00:05:00,766
Apart from that, this young heroine
just saved my life.

66
00:05:02,566 --> 00:05:04,533
I forgot to introduce myself.

67
00:05:04,666 --> 00:05:08,066
I am the secretary
of WE Beauty Family, Jin Xi'en.

68
00:05:08,066 --> 00:05:11,333
Hello, I am the representative
of Lihuai International, Zeng Huaishi.

69
00:05:12,300 --> 00:05:13,500
Personal secretary.

70
00:05:15,133 --> 00:05:16,199
Personal?

71
00:05:17,133 --> 00:05:18,699
Interesting.

72
00:05:18,766 --> 00:05:22,066
Since you're the boss of my savior,
let me propose a toast.

73
00:05:22,066 --> 00:05:23,999
I'll visit your company sometime.

74
00:05:25,300 --> 00:05:26,400
You are always welcome.

75
00:05:26,600 --> 00:05:28,666
Welcome to visit and give instructions.

76
00:05:31,600 --> 00:05:33,728
You can go on. I'll go over there.

77
00:05:35,533 --> 00:05:36,640
By the way, Mr. Lan,

78
00:05:37,500 --> 00:05:39,584
if your group can't get
Series B financing again,

79
00:05:40,233 --> 00:05:41,966
you won't be able to hold on, right?

80
00:05:45,600 --> 00:05:47,333
You are underestimating our group.

81
00:06:00,466 --> 00:06:01,200
Gu Qianqian?

82
00:06:02,133 --> 00:06:05,399
Ma'am, I understand.

83
00:06:06,033 --> 00:06:10,666
Why not sincerely kneel down?

84
00:06:11,300 --> 00:06:14,800
Miss Gu, it has nothing to do
with my mother.

85
00:06:14,800 --> 00:06:16,256
Please don't make it hard for her.

86
00:06:17,696 --> 00:06:19,699
Are you schizophrenic?

87
00:06:21,300 --> 00:06:23,300
You were so arrogant just now,

88
00:06:23,633 --> 00:06:24,999
and now you're backing down.

89
00:06:26,266 --> 00:06:29,599
Your mother didn't teach you
to be responsible for your behaviors.

90
00:06:29,600 --> 00:06:30,766
Today, I'll teach you.

91
00:06:34,166 --> 00:06:36,400
Now you know why there was
that arranged marriage, right?

92
00:06:39,100 --> 00:06:41,733
Gu Qianqian is Zeng Huaishi's cousin.
Don't act rashly.

93
00:06:43,400 --> 00:06:44,833
Your family is really pathetic.

94
00:06:47,900 --> 00:06:50,733
Qianqian, who is this?

95
00:06:50,733 --> 00:06:52,933
A little bunny.

96
00:06:52,933 --> 00:06:54,432
A poorly educated

97
00:06:55,424 --> 00:06:57,866
rude bunny that is clumsy.

98
00:06:59,936 --> 00:07:03,939
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

99
00:07:03,939 --> 00:07:08,096
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

100
00:07:08,512 --> 00:07:14,208
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪

101
00:07:15,476 --> 00:07:19,998
♪I pass through the crowd with you♪

102
00:07:23,028 --> 00:07:27,989
♪As if we have a tacit understanding,
attracting each other♪

103
00:07:31,038 --> 00:07:36,862
♪When the loneliness cracks,
warmth seeps in♪

104
00:07:36,862 --> 00:07:43,488
♪You come with light,
shining into my heart♪

105
00:07:44,332 --> 00:07:47,813
♪Stars fall into my eyes,
and you fall into my heart♪

106
00:07:47,813 --> 00:07:51,934
♪I make a wish foolishly,
but actually, you are the shooting star♪

107
00:07:51,934 --> 00:07:53,630
♪Open my secret♪

108
00:07:53,630 --> 00:07:59,678
♪I hope you find
all the tenderness hidden for you♪

109
00:07:59,678 --> 00:08:03,550
♪Sinking into your love,
I want to sink deeper♪

110
00:08:03,550 --> 00:08:08,056
♪With each breath,
I can feel the sweetness♪

111
00:08:09,952 --> 00:08:16,766
♪Two lonely islands meet,
and it's the gift of fate♪
